Package: FindFocals
Type: Package
Title: Find focal gains & deletions in SNP array data
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2017-09-05
Author: Bernat Gel <bgel@igtp.cat>
Maintainer: Bernat Gel <bgel@igtp.cat>
Description: A simple package to detect small focal gains and deletions in SNP
    array data. It uses a naive approach to find clusters of SNPs above or 
    below the expected range.
License: Artistic-2.0
Depends:
    R (>= 3.4),
    regioneR,
    karyoploteR
Imports:
    DNAcopy,
    zoo,
    GenomicRanges,
    GenomeInfoDb
Suggests:
    BiocStyle,
    knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
